snippet.title: Contagion VR: Outbreak - Biotec Trailer!
snippet.description:
The long awaited mission 4 Biotec, here we tease the new mission. End of April 2020! This will be a free downloadable release for the main game and the last stepping stone of Early Access! 

Follow us on our social media!
https://www.facebook.com/contagion.outbreak.game
https://twitter.com/ContOutbreak
https://discord.gg/Monochrome

Available on Steam, Oculus, Viveport and PSVR!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/676840/Contagion_VR_Outbreak/

https://www.oculus.com/experiences/rift/1859059894211295/

https://www.viveport.com/apps/940d409e-c617-47a8-8ba7-46f5bd2cdf53/Contagion_VR:_Outbreak/

https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/contagion-vr-outbreak-ps4/#buynow
